## 🛠️ Hands-on Exercise: Your First Touch of Cloud

Try this out:

- [ ] Identify a cloud-based app you use daily (e.g. Gmail, OneDrive)
- [ ] Classify it: IaaS / PaaS / SaaS?
- [ ] What deployment model is it using?
- [ ] List 3 benefits you personally experience

📬 Share your answers in the [Issues](../../issues) section of this repo!

